Description of male. Head : (
Fig. 1
) Lateral lobe truncate; inferior antennal sinus shallow; eyes reniform, medium, not reaching top of head.

Ecology. Common among submerged aquatic vegetation and assorted algae in low salinity bays, bayous, and estuaries; subtidal, rarely intertidal in marshes (
Thomas 1976
;
Heard 1982
;
LeCroy 2000
).
